name: Dreaming of Doors
description:
From the 100 Days of Drawing Series //

This 2021 personal challenge started in early March. The goal, to produce a finished piece, everyday, for 100 days  //

"The inhabitants of the dawn mist looked over her. She dreamed of doors in the mountains. She would find one 7 days later, cursed by fire"
